Flavours & Dining

Catering & Menus

   Our restaurant is both refined and friendly, and is guaranteed to
   satisfy even the most demanding customers. Enjoy the views across the
   grounds, flower-lined gardens and ancient trees from the windows of the
   dining rooms.

   Our chef's range of exquisite dishes, made from natural ingredients and
   using authentic, genuine flavours, is guaranteed to set your taste buds
   alight. Our recipes are made using produce from our own vegetable
   garden, local farms and small producers, as well as Label Rouge
   Charolais meats and the freshest fish available. We place a particular
   emphasis on the use of organically produced ingredients.

   Our dishes change according to the latest harvests, with a seasonal
   menu and a Market Produce menu that changes every day.
   Read more Close

